<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She's looking younger by the day.</p>

<p>And Sonja Morgan exuded extreme confidence as she posted a makeup-free selfie to Instagram on Tuesday morning.</p>

<p>The 56-year-old reality television star was glowing in the fresh-faced snap just months after receiving a lower facelift to freshen up her look.</p>

<p>Stunning: Sonja Morgan exuded extreme confidence as she posted a makeup-free selfie to Instagram on Tuesday morning</p>

<p>Sonja credited the local scenery for her dewy demeanor in a photo from vacation at the Casa Salles Hotel Boutique in Tequila, Jalisco, Mexico.</p>

<p>'I know you guys like when I share a pic without makeup. So here’s one from a recent vacation to <?php echo e('@'); ?>casasalleshotel,' she wrote. 'Something in the volcano water there. I slept so well.'</p>

<p>The Real Housewives of New York star certainly looked refreshed and could claim a little bit of help after going under the knife.</p>

<p>Younger than ever: The Real Housewives of New York star certainly looked refreshed and could claim a little bit of help after going under the knife</p>

<p>'There’s been speculation around my fresh new look. I got a lower facelift and neck lift after wrapping Season 12,' she captioned a snap in July</p>

<p>'There’s been speculation around my fresh new look. I got a lower facelift and neck lift after wrapping Season 12,' she captioned a snap in July.</p>

<p>'I just wanted to be rid of the wrinkling on my neck and the jowels that were starting to form. People thought I was nuts because it was so subtle. But not to me!</p>

<p>'It was a no-brainer – gravity had taken its toll, I was also exhausted and I needed a “pick me up”. I entrusted my face to the best <?php echo e('@'); ?>drjacono  and he hit it out of the park.'</p>

<p>Best in the biz: Sonja joined the housewives cast nearly one decade ago for season three and has since climbed the ranks to be a fan favorite</p>

<p>Sonja recently chatted with DailyMailTV about putting her infamous Manhattan townhouse on the market for a cool $8.75million.</p>

<p>The renovated Lennox Hill home in Manhattan was originally built in 1899 and features five bedrooms and five bathrooms.</p>

<p>Ever the gracious seller, Morgan slashed $2million from the price for a special 'COVID discount.' </p>

